hagia (Umemoto et al., \n2020). Regarding its severity, it will depend on the stage of PD and, in \nA.B.R. Leite Silva et al.", page:5}}, {_id:2595, properties:{chunk_index:0, id:"1-s2.0-S1568163722002768-main.pdf::p6::0::f20a78f7", embedding:[0.022271995, 0.0798057, -0.15657088, -0.054933075, 0.032556277, 0.024386635, -0.025125269, 0.0129867345, 0.051125817, -0.06919708, -0.014274092, 0.036757257, 0.07410598, 0.024362462, -0.031635925, -0.05156262, 0.010572509, -0.07865813, -0.06329502, 0.065473, -0.05860968, 5.7579606E-4, -0.028029095, -0.056988012, 0.026158154, 0.06886137, -0.02460001, 0.024399789, 0.035850924, 0.0328258, 0.100442424, -0.046891302, 0.015664447, -0.010952354, -0.0714021, -0.02033961, 0.085305974, 0.048650745, 0.04778028, 0.03247349, 0.03795272, -0.015962254, 0.0019659786, -0.061605614, -0.04627573, 0.028448785, 0.006531649, 0.041814074, 0.0132068945, -0.019828824, 0.024095045, -0.079742454, -0.032205373, -0.014951839, 0.048867848, 0.0042954492, -0.065198205, -0.028494982, 0.0022039758, -0.072836176, 0.07442875, 0.014437258, -0.023697976, 0.055526897, 0.071960695, -0.044805624, -0.007713729, 0.040509567, 0.01637083, -0.029415302, 0.02776828, -0.0033078808, -0.010593556, 0.008301811, -0.037069883, 0.05438438, -0.002078683, 0.0060577206, -0.003698233, -0.009481815, -6.238454E-4, 0.03662131, 0.054984156, 0.033109263, 0.06933785, -0.024078514, 0.0063549136, 0.0053994404, 0.038863286, 0.07412974, 0.008984067, 0.01997828, 0.002906003, 0.034781408, -0.02956448, 0.0057749227, 0.023641456, -0.013012052, -0.024024913, -0.01678341, -0.04056903, 0.0057563935, -0.009050481, 0.0050235237, 0.047955997, 0.047162876, 0.030986853, 0.026583672, -0.0116104605, -0.014086673, -0.06742408, 0.07775942, 0.0051760124, -0.03615702, 0.050674934, 8.861227E-4, 0.04099779, -0.023975166, -0.019791571, 0.034182146, -0.053538896, -0.019217135, 0.013317514, 0.03716814, 0.003269205, 0.0071136425, -0.033153825, 0.004751618, 0.016753616, 0.008646486, -0.025983434, -0.0149365775, -0.040