ms & Wilkins, Cambridge Uni­\nversity Press, and Springer. He cofounded REGAIN Therapeutics and is \nco-inventor of the patent “Compositions and methods for treatment \nand/or prophylaxis of proteinopathies.” He serves on the editorial \nA.J. Espay and A.J. Lees", page:5}}, {_id:2877, properties:{chunk_index:0, id:"1-s2.0-S1353802024000890-main.pdf::p6::0::e1291630", embedding:[0.0409062, 0.08755161, -0.16183724, -0.045953322, 0.052109424, -0.036782783, 0.024074208, 0.050968003, 0.0047571585, -0.04165612, -0.020501433, 0.029805563, 0.08231601, 0.005053746, 0.0048701037, -0.054241855, -0.028466282, -0.047735352, -0.05018743, 0.05164074, -0.038855948, -0.029942675, 0.011667863, -0.01013364, 0.059150133, 0.07756112, -0.037683696, -0.03372806, 0.043059606, 0.0034610345, 0.096125945, -0.023252018, 0.007461051, -0.034519304, -0.02296266, -0.026236447, 0.04846095, -0.002535531, 0.006343668, 0.013965151, -0.017315201, 0.0347534, -0.010754765, -0.07340602, -3.0396233E-4, 0.022072291, 0.041022602, -0.031653352, 0.075506374, -0.06268824, 0.03153319, -0.008529053, 0.005306969, -0.041834284, 0.0728659, 0.02995178, 0.00983564, -0.020121252, 0.0117541505, -0.003327728, 0.055885196, 0.0585025, -0.02700301, 0.0064847264, 0.07020526, -0.046136174, -0.0017646457, 0.089145064, 0.020938557, -0.051391102, 0.06926873, -0.010901572, -0.0019419064, 0.03658056, -0.016549792, 0.018102951, 0.038205888, -0.0027759296, 0.0052333595, 0.017180772, 6.848369E-4, -0.012041745, 0.030342374, 0.04938157, 0.048233252, 0.007086248, -0.089582115, 0.017665587, -0.061686546, 0.049736857, 0.055242248, 0.0126553215, 0.007960174, 0.010857403, -0.0403617, 0.014728302, 0.05117252, 0.015920985, -0.0413053, -0.0028249482, -0.036373693, -0.025231894, -0.010864602, -0.012434796, 0.037223, 0.054680847, 0.04488593, -0.021388097, -0.0038113338, -0.0038520137, -0.039221834, 0.035903808, -0.033481024, -0.011364184, 0.031394023, 0.025672965, 0.01511952, -0.039389163, -0.015695218, 0.062163603, 0.022238037, -0.048499793, 0.